{"tid":366742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望平時做開gym 既你地們可以黎解答同埋俾啲建議，感激","createTime":"2017-08-20T08:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T00:30:40.000Z","uid":129558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c55e94a7508aa730155b49aeefb9c250e59bb4","tid":366742,"uid":129558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"希望入黎既你地可以認真解答我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從呢兩個星期開始做返gym 同跑步，<br />\n我食量俾之前多左好多好多，<br />\n我冇飲奶粉，<br />\n跑步一個星期最少都跑1-2次<br />\n平時係屋企做gym，一個禮拜3-4次，時間大概45分鐘，手臂，胸，腹都會做，<br />\n做完之後會食4隻雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n到第二日開始就會好想食野...直到依架都係咁<br />\n早餐都係食蛋（2-3隻），<br />\n但到公司就會開始肚餓，<br />\n之後就算我食完lunch 大概3個鐘之後就會開始想食野...<br />\n<br />\n我想問以上情況正唔正常？<br />\n同埋我上網搵過好多飲食控制，選擇實在太多啦⋯⋯我唔識揀<br />\n同埋我想問個飲食餐單應該係點？<br />\n<br />\n你地可唔可以俾啲建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659192477c50babc154fca758136ee56c6693ae9","tid":366742,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"搵個目標比自己先<br />\n你係想減肥？六舊朱古力？大胸肌？個膊頭橫d?<br />\n搵到目標再深入操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個星期三日已經好夠<br />\n同埋最緊要係食同訓<br />\n操得足訓唔夠都唔會大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦底就唔好跑步<br />\n會越跑越瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2413e2e624f7d63a12589b78ddf553389b3f3ab0","tid":366742,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"瘦底？"},{"pid":"89c6da771e992d779169f8824f858624ae47ce84","tid":366742,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瘦底？</blockquote><br />\n大波?"},{"pid":"be1a203b6c4cfcaebc866ba9298fcb19f28367c4","tid":366742,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"想手臂同個胸大D<br />\n依家大腿正常人 不過個身好撚瘦"},{"pid":"f9e1ff7336d78f387217d72c53c8e80f0ae66e7d","tid":366742,"uid":129558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵個目標比自己先<br />\n你係想減肥？六舊朱古力？大胸肌？個膊頭橫d?<br />\n搵到目標再深入操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個星期三日已經好夠<br />\n同埋最緊要係食同訓<br />\n操得足訓唔夠都唔會大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦底就唔好跑步<br />\n會越跑越瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 其實我最主要係想要腹肌，<br />\n因為我有肚腩<br />\n同埋你知唔知點樣減走體脂肪？"},{"pid":"67d37e763b330f2c06af5b44be01f0a707fa6cc5","tid":366742,"uid":129558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瘦底？</blockquote><br />\nNo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58da8bfcb24b1de55d328ce06220c24787ed8cf9","tid":366742,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵個目標比自己先<br />\n你係想減肥？六舊朱古力？大胸肌？個膊頭橫d?<br />\n搵到目標再深入操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個星期三日已經好夠<br />\n同埋最緊要係食同訓<br />\n操得足訓唔夠都唔會大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦底就唔好跑步<br />\n會越跑越瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 其實我最主要係想要腹肌，<br />\n因為我有肚腩<br />\n同埋你知唔知點樣減走體脂肪？</blockquote><br />\n先重訓後帶氧 減脂靠帶氧 咪聽d傻尻講脂肪變肌肉 做sit up 會firm左唔代表瘦"},{"pid":"57faccf90bafacfe6730a6fb05e85b02bb1942d6","tid":366742,"uid":90634,"like":0,"disli